songs.title: Never Scared
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Lil Mosey]
Yuh, yuh
Ooh, ooh
Ayy Royce
Ayy Royce
Ayy Royce
Ayy Royce, you did it right here

[Chorus: Lil Mosey]
Wrist nigga to the right, you broke get over there
I was really runnin' since a baby, was never scared
I'm the biggest nigga in my city could be the mayor
And I'm sold on lean, but I'm still gonna say a prayer
I been getting bread now
Got new chain, and bust-down
Ask me how I got here, yeah, I don't know how
Now a nigga up, yeah, they know now
All my niggas are reckless, yeah
What are you about?

[Verse 1: Lil Mosey]
All my diamonds glistening (Yeah, they glistening)
Take a brick, then I I'm flippin' (Yeah, I'm flippin)
Like a hoe, I was whippin' (Skrrt, skrrt)
I got a cast and I'm drippin' (Yeah, I'm drippin')
Yeah, Balmain jeans and I'm rockin' (I'm rockin)
I got deals but I'm still fucking flockin' (Yeah I'm flockin')
Nigga you are broke, stop talking (Stop talking)
Drippin' watch so I had to fuck on moshpit

[Chorus: Lil Mosey]
Wrist nigga to the right, you broke get over there
I was really runnin' since a baby, was never scared
I'm the biggest nigga in my city could be the mayor
And I'm sold on lean, but I'm still gonna say a prayer
I been getting bread now
Got new chain, and bust-down
Ask me how I got here, yeah, I don't know how
Now a nigga up, yeah, they know now
All my niggas are reckless, yeah
What are you about?

[Verse 2: Lil Mosey]
Diamonds hittin' hard with no flash, yeah
When I had no bread, I stayed with mash, yeah
Versus all my niggas, you get last, yeah
We go get this money then we dash, yeah
I be smokin' big dope, it's a fact now (smokin' gas)
Fuckin' with my nigga, we lay you flat down, yeah
If you talkin' stupid, you get smacked out
I got hoes on me, I brought my racks out (lil' bitch)
Talkin' like you got bread, you got nothing
We ran down on you, you started running
Never been a bitch, I never fall in
I can't fuck with rats, I'm never talkin'

[Chorus: Lil Mosey]
Wrist nigga to the right, you broke get over there
I was really runnin' since a baby, was never scared
I'm the biggest nigga in my city could be the mayor
And I'm sold on lean, but I'm still gonna say a prayer
I been getting bread now
Got new chain, and bust-down
Ask me how I got here, yeah, I don't know how
Now a nigga up, yeah, they know now
All my niggas are reckless, yeah
What are you about?

[Verse 3: Trippie Redd]
Unknown

[Outro: Lil Mosey]
Brrr
